After her husband's death, she 
reported called a cleaner to deal with the blood-soaked carpets. 'She 
didn't seem at all upset,' neighbour Michael Rudchenko said.

Alan Goodman's death was originally 
ruled suspicious by police, but investigators could not determine if 
